Package org.tantalum.j2me

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    J2MEImageTypeHandler
    This is a helper class for creating an image class.
    J2MELog
    Debug-time logging implementation for J2ME To enable logging from a phone connected to a computer by a USB cable, open a terminal emulator on the window, set the COM port parameters in Windows Devices, and call L.startUSBDebugging() at program start.
    J2MEPlatformUtils
    Utilities for support of each specific platform (J2ME, Android, ..) The platform-specific local copy of this class replaces this base version for other platforms.
    J2MEPlatformUtils.J2MEHttpConn
    A convenience class abstracting HTTP connection operations between different platforms
    RMSCache
    Persistent storage implementation for J2ME
    RMSUtils
    RMS Utility methods
    TantalumMIDlet
    This is a convenience class to embody the best practice patterns for starting and stopping an app which uses Tantalum.
